body:
I'm suspicious of this code:

```csharp
public static string GetContentRoot()
{
    var currentDirectory = Directory.GetCurrentDirectory();
    var webSiteRelativePath = @"..\..\..\..\BasicWebSite\";

    return Path.Combine(currentDirectory, webSiteRelativePath);
}
```

It would be better to use a known location (like `typeof(WebSite).Assembly.Location`) rather than `Directory.GetCurrentDirectory()`.
